  "detailed_description": "<h1>为您推荐的LSP新作</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/0355a124d8011af760a4aeb6b53b91a3.avif?t=1773754523\" width=600 height=528 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/cb9a4c9804996571eed91e1983984af6.avif?t=1773754523\" width=616 height=112 /></span><br>24岁的自由职业画师男主，与住在自己隔壁的23岁OL女主偶然邂逅——<br>当男主发现女主竟然是分开了多年，曾被自己误认为是男生的儿时玩伴后，虽然意外，但两人的关系也以此为契机熟络了起来。<br>后经历过一系列的误会、矛盾、互助和相互扶持的相处后，两人的感情逐步升温——直到夏日旅行后两人正式开始了以结婚为前提的交往。<br>最终，女主辞掉了工作，和男主一起组建了一个小小的独立游戏工作室，为了实现儿时的愿望一边撒狗粮一边努力着.....<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/79810a3390d149bcd7a1b5fe6e9e526b.avif?t=1773754523\" width=616 height=112 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/79844685d3ebd083f2a615f3d9ab95d9.poster.avif?t=1773754523\" width=600 height=464 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/79844685d3ebd083f2a615f3d9ab95d9.webm?t=1773754523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/79844685d3ebd083f2a615f3d9ab95d9.mp4?t=1773754523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/71252ab283c3b92208b9f2d65b7db735.poster.avif?t=1773754523\" width=600 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475040/extras/71252ab283c3b92208b9f2d65b7db735.webm?t=1773754523